WEBVTT

1
00:26:35.840 --> 00:26:38.170 
我不想打断你们  但是...
I hate to interrupt you, but the reason we're here...

2
00:26:38.260 --> 00:26:40.220 
有样东西我希望你能看一下
Yes. I have something to show you.

3
00:26:40.300 --> 00:26:42.100 
我留你父亲自己在图书馆工作
I left your father working in the library.

4
00:26:42.180 --> 00:26:45.270 
当时他请我去拿旧都市计划图
He sent me to the map section to fetch an ancient plan of the city.

5
00:26:45.350 --> 00:26:48.180 
我回来时发现他跟文件不见了
When I got back to his table, he'd gone, with all his papers,

6
00:26:48.270 --> 00:26:50.770 
只剩下这张纸  在他的椅子旁边发现的
except for that scrap, which I found near his chair.

7
00:26:50.850 --> 00:26:52.350 
是罗马数字
Roman numerals.

8
00:26:52.480 --> 00:26:54.230 
图书馆到了
Here is the library.

9
00:26:54.610 --> 00:26:57.240 
它看起来一点都不像图书馆
That doesn't look much like a library.

10
00:26:57.490 --> 00:26:59.450 
比较像是教堂
Looks like a converted church.

11
00:26:59.530 --> 00:27:01.610 
一点都没错
In this case, it's the literal truth.

12
00:27:01.700 --> 00:27:03.450 
你们来到了圣地
We are on holy ground.

13
00:27:03.530 --> 00:27:07.160 
这些柱子饱受战火蹂躏  之后被送来这里
These columns over here were brought back as spoils of war

